markets.title: Will America profit in any month of 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If the Monthly Treasury Statement (MTS) reports a surplus for any month in 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The month surplus can be found in the column labeled "Current Month Deficit Surplus Amount" in the the table "Summary of Receipts, Outlays, and Surplus or Deficit” in the MTS (see: https://fiscaldata.treasury.gov/datasets/monthly-treasury-statement/summary-of-receipts-outlays-and-the-deficit-surplus-of-the-u-s-government).
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close early if the event occurs or after all the data is released.
